左叶秋生 发表于 2020-3-19 16:43
这个 大大你看看怎么解决
直接删除 匠魂扩充.jar 吧

或者在 .minecraft\config\pewter\pewter.cfg 中设置

"material blacklist:" {
    # Blacklist for Pewter Materials. Add the materials you don't want and they will not be loaded on startup [default: ]
    S:materialBlacklist <
    thaumium
     >
}
